author: 123MrBrick
title: Good for MOCs, not much else...
review:
This set is an okay EPI AAT. However, i imagine that the tan parts would be much more useful for MOCs.

Box/Instructions

The set comes in a standard polybag. Nothing too fancy.

Parts

This set comes with a fairly basic selection of parts, but many of them are in tan for the first time, I believe.

Minifigures

N/A.

The build

Building the set takes around 2-3 minutes. Nothing too complicated.

The completed model

The finished product looks good, but it doesn't scale with the polybag MTT. The turret does swivel, however.

Overall opinion

Overall, I would only get this if you are a MOCer. No one really likes The Phantom Menace anyways.
